{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A terrifying killer clown terrorizes a teenager and his family on Halloween Eve.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A short but very action-packed horror game awaits you.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161920/extras/3.gif?t=1729084980\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You play as a stubborn teenager. Your parents punished you and locked you in your room. They called a nanny to keep an eye on you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It's night outside, Halloween is in full swing, and on TV there is a report about a maniac in a clown costume who escaped from prison...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161920/extras/2.gif?t=1729084980\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Hi all! My name is Romooll and I am 14 years old. This is my first experience in developing a game and I really hope you like it. When creating the game, I collected all my teenage experiences and fears, added a little of myself to the main character and tried to create a truly creepy atmosphere for the game on Halloween.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in this dark story and try to survive the terrible night with the main character. Experience all the horror that a person can experience in such a situation and try not to scream in fear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>In the game you will have to find and use different things and carefully follow the plot clues. Listen to what the characters say and move forward in the story./u]</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u></u><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161920/extras/1__1_.gif?t=1729084980\" /><u></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>GAME FEATURES:</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>- Realistic graphics</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>- Excellent sound design</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>- Well-developed horror atmosphere</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>- Possibility to make a pumpkin for Halloween</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>The approximate time to complete the game is 50 minutes.</strong></u></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"HIT HARDER!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3161920/62e133e21b1c1b82bd4365a815b4eb835dbb1bdd.jpg"},{"name":"COOL MUSICIAN","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3161920/d783098ca06da1db661acba6bee77ced9a9f66d7.jpg"},{"name":"DID YOU TRY","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3161920/7b4b2de3f9fbc8facdb8f56ecc20b8aea2027fb3.jpg"},{"name":"BANG!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3161920/6df1907634f2a4f148593891a6fb996ded670ac9.jpg"},{"name":"YOU ARE VERY BRAVE!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3161920/41127ac68a32e91eb725f027841d72612e36012d.jpg"},{"name":"RUN FAST!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3161920/821eb56a3c0532be373fa6c8205c54d490e9d5aa.jpg"}],"total":6},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161920/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729084980","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161920/page.bg.jpg?t=1729084980","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161920/476fcfc9612d62f3d5fa6b23a93bcdb67fe744c0/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729084980","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161920/476fcfc9612d62f3d5fa6b23a93bcdb67fe744c0/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1729084980","categories":[{"description":"Sing